Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:17.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:18.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰火？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:19.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:20.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是之前的那个事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第五起了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前一样爆炸本身的规模不大并没有产生伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:02.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作为愉快犯来说还真让人笑不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs15}愉快犯:  制造骚乱以从中取乐的犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  关于嫌犯的线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:13.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  终于找到线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  您听说过「虚空爆炸」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(393,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虚空爆炸」…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指重力子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪起事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:28.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爆炸之前通过卫星都观测到了重力子的急促的加速运动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如将铝罐作为基点将重力子以爆炸性的速度加速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:35.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在瞬间往四周扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:39.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说把铝罐变成了炸弹  这个就是原理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是铝罐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:45.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道这是能力者的所作所为了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话只需查一下学院都市的「书库」不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:56.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为所有学生的能力数据都记录在案了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然已经搜查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所答复的能力是「量子变速」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Synchrotron
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:06.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且能力还要足够将铝罐变为炸弹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有一名大能力的学生能符合条件了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那个人就是嫌犯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她有不在场证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:16.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人一直住着院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:19.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能引起这一连串的事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是又无解了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书库的数据应该也不会有缺漏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:33.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是还有没记录在案的能力者什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我也去帮忙去找嫌犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才是不是想着「这个说不定会有趣呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:50.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「根据对手强弱我也能一试身手」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事怎么可…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装傻也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子我早就看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我很早就跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人怎么说也是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:02.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持治安的活动就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们风纪委员就行了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:12.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为带着不严肃的好奇心和兴趣就能胜任风纪委员那就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:12.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了  我没打算这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请你在此时此地发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  不许随随便便地趟这起事件的混水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  这算什么啊  这种单方面的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:30.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二  即使万一不幸被卷入事件当中  也严禁单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待风纪委员的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为  你们来之前事情都已经解决…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三  不许在裙子底下穿短裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟这个无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:45.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籍此机会顺便从服装和其他种种生活态度上重新审视自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:51.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  姐姐大人非常缺乏作为常盘台的王牌的自觉这点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:52.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子也感到非常担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  请让我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您有些许自觉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:02.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会抱着玩具熊睡觉  往浴缸里放橡皮鸭什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该从这种小孩子的兴趣当中毕业了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那彩色调的幼稚内衣和睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说也是学园都市第三的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名声在外的「超电磁炮」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(298,326)}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我老妈吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢初春同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之能先坐下吗  御坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:38.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是推测  白井同学只是不想御坂学姐卷入危险当中而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「虚空爆炸事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有这个名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始只是垃圾桶里面的空罐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  常常发现玩偶及小孩子的包包等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易让人放松警惕的物品中被放入了铝金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还做得真过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:59.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不一定是因为这原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但白井同学的确很担心御坂学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是您的巨人水果冰淇淋杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初～春～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白…白井同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:22.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这里偷懒胆子还真不小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  跟我去巡逻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  冻糕还…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻糕还…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我让初春陪我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见就跟我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是风纪委员的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是普通人别随便插嘴的意思么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘记了吗姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:50.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员的工作没姐姐想像的那样轻松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:50.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…冻糕…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  那么嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上老是挂着风纪委员风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment  Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么至少在我把不良少年干掉之前赶来一次看看啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这样也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会再还给她就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么悠闲地在这偷什么懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧  被派来增援的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  那个…你说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实刚才把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快点把臂章带上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  走  走去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你到底怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  是没见过的脸孔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是新人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我是从今天开始配属到此的御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:01.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂…御坂…好像在哪听说过的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请问前辈名叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是177支部的固法美伟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教！  固法前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让她见识一下我也是能够胜任风纪委员的工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(431,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么枪林箭雨尽管给我打过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:19.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是扫把啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们收到了打扫这里的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:35.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…那个  我是风纪委员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:35.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(383,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:40.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊  学生们乱丢的垃圾由我们风纪委员来收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:40.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(433,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实习的时候没学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  说起来的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员的工作就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这个也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了  给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:14.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我的厉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:25.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然忘记带臂章  不谨慎也得有个限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是没看到类似的东西  也没寄放在柜台上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检讨书先别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时回到支部取备用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行  像那样随便使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么「但是」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保卫治安和风纪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行使武力是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  的确在实习当中…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我在实习的内容之前  先以普通的常识来考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员的工作可没有那么轻松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会认真做好工作给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…嗯  那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:39.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…我根本不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:51.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然实习和现场工作有很大差别吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  真没有想到  自己会连看地图都一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有轻重  甚至连察言观色都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原来也不擅长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于地图的查看方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是熟悉的街道  也意外的费工夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  我是固法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我们也会帮忙寻找的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到寻找失物的请求了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:25.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找失物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  好像是个包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:33.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  常常发现玩偶及小孩子的包包等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:36.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易让人放松警惕的物品中被放入了铝金属
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非是小孩子用的包包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这都被你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是粉红色的  上面还有花朵的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:48.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是放在长椅上的时候被狗叼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那可不得了  得赶紧把那只狗抓住才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要是途中被丢弃的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:58.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会被谁捡走带回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十万火急  得赶紧把包找回来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  我没办法穿过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我也是勉勉强强才能挪动…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:24.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂同学  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像有一条腿很多的虫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  到底跑到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:38.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像有一条没有腿的虫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:53.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  又不是在找猫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想都找错地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂同学  再往右一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:06.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…这样乱动的话…我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:11.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  D地区也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:15.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  感谢你们的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  初春在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  这里是风纪委员第177支部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首让我好找的歌  总算被我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经累得睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春已经有孩子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  她什么时候才会长出花来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是长出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说那里么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  我才没有生宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:50.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看的话  你俩的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  再不安静点就要把她吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪佐天同学乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:03.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  她是来委托我们帮她找包的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:12.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是父母送给她的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:15.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在委托其他支部帮忙寻找期间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:18.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我和白井同学负责照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  居然需要向其他支部求援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得有些小题大做么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:28.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园都市的人不是基本都和家人分开了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:32.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种事  大家都会倍显积极哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员的工作还真不简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞了人后连一句道歉的话也不会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你随便开口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:15.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里没事了  你们两个人合起来干这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:16.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍…忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:26.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会早点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:39.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说还没有找过的地方的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这里很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  也可能会有怕狗的小孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是怕不怕狗的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  万一被咬的话可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  事情没那么简单吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们开始找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂同学就负责那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:10.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐是风纪委员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:20.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是常盘台中学的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子下面居然穿着短裤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要穿这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是身为大小姐的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有普通的内裤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿在短裤里面了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:35.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没穿内裤～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没穿内裤的风纪委员～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:52.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:03.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别把我看扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅  不愧是常盘台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:19.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:21.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样粗率地拿着不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不联络爆破物处理组的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆破物？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  可别再弄丢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:39.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是固法前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到它的并不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你们认识御坂同学么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么认不认识的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是御坂美琴啊  就是常盘台中学的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:01.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂…美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个「超电磁炮」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么御坂学姐会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:09.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿成那副样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:14.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为  她为了保护包而奋不顾身地跳进了喷水池
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:18.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是误将包认作是炸弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:24.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明都跟姐姐大人说到那个份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  或许这才符合御坂学姐的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑…黑子  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要那么慌张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘台的超电磁炮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  露馅了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:00.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可真够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是您自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:23.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一赌气就跑去假装风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:23.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底要孩子气到什么程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必好好反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员的工作可真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是真的对黑子刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不枉我苦等至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请对我刮目相看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的每一寸肌肤都尽收眼底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  此刮目非彼刮目啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  来吧  来吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:41.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:41.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:44.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即从这里撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:46.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问  我的店里出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.29,0:22:49.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们观测到重力子的活动加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:50.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店有被安置了炸弹的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸…炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:22:58.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  到底在哪里
